creator: Parallel Realities
descriptionHtml:
Fill in the square with the numbers 1 through 9 so that the arithmetic matches the numbers at the end of each row and column.

Features

* Simple controls
* Fun for all ages from 8 to 80
* Educational
* BODMAS / BEDMAS support
* 5 difficulty levels
descriptionShort: Fill in the square to solve the math problems

title: Math Square

creator: Parallel Realities
descriptionHtml:
Fill in the square with the numbers 1 through 9 so that the arithmetic matches the numbers at the end of each row and column.

Optional BODMAS / BEDMAS / BIDMAS / Order of Operations support, i.e.

9 + 6 * 5 = 39 (BODMAS) or 9 + 6 * 5 = 75 (no BODMAS)

Features

* Simple controls
* Fun for all ages from 8 to 80
* Educational
* BODMAS / BEDMAS support
* 5 difficulty levels
descriptionShort: Fill in the square to solve the math problems

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Fixed a bug whereby in certain circumstances a puzzle would be flagged as correct even though there was still a cell to fill in. This only happened when playing on the non-BODMAS (or, as someone described it ,"thicko") mode.
